name: com.castsoftware.aip.console.tools
title: AIP Console integration tools
description:
Package containing the AIP Console Jenkins Plugin and AIP Console Tools CLI.

            These components aims to help automating application on-boarding and/or analysis in AIP Console.

            If you need more details about the AIP Console Jenkins Plugin, you can check the following page :
            https://github.com/CAST-Extend/com.castsoftware.uc.aip.console.tools/blob/develop/aip-console-jenkins/README.md

            If you need details about the AIP Console Tools CLI, you can find them here :
            https://github.com/CAST-Extend/com.castsoftware.uc.aip.console.tools/blob/develop/aip-console-tools-cli/README.md
